      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "@raffian Problems can occur if you don&#39;t transform all the character data in one go. See <a href=\"http://illegalargumentexception.blogspot.co.uk/2009/05/java-rough-guide-to-character-encoding.html#javaencoding_stringclass\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">here</a> for an example."
