      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Yes, bit of a gotcha! For Gradle, Maven users: <i>&quot;commons-codec:commons-codec:1.10&quot;</i> (at time of writing).  This also comes bundled as a dependency with Apache POI, for example.  Apart from that Apache Commons to the rescue, as ever!"
